      "longDescription": "Electronic Examination Hall – Al-Imam Mohammad Ibn Saud Islamic University Design & Build by ELC Contracting (Turnkey Project) ELC Contracting delivered a complete turnkey solution for the Electronic Examination Hall at Al-Imam University, designed specifically to host academic final exams with high efficiency. Project Scope: Main Examination Hall: Comprehensive fit-out of the hall, optimized for electronic final examinations, ensuring a quiet and organized environment for students. Installation of advanced power and data infrastructure to support hundreds of exam stations simultaneously. Entrances & Flow Management: Design and execution of the hall entrances to manage the high traffic of students during exam periods smoothly. Visual Identity (Signage & Branding): Application of university branding through wall graphics and directional signage to guide students to their exam seats. Reception & Support Area: Construction of a fully equipped reception counter to assist students and proctors before and during exams.",
