      "id": "project-2",
      "description": "The Face Shop",
      "longDescription": "The Face Shop Project | Execution by ELC Contracting ELC Contracting is proud to have executed the fit-out for The Face Shop, the leading Korean skincare brand. The project was delivered as a Turnkey Solution, with strict adherence to the brand’s global visual identity that blends nature with modern aesthetics. Execution & Engineering Highlights: Facade & Branding: Installation of a full-span transparent glass facade to provide a panoramic view of the showroom. Execution of the illuminated signage in the brand’s signature green, utilizing high-clarity LED technology. Fixtures & Displays: Fabrication and installation of wall-mounted shelving units, combining black metal frames with light-toned wood for a modern, organized look. Execution of the central \"Display Island,\" featuring integrated storage drawers and smooth wooden surfaces for product testing. Flooring & Lighting: Installation of high-quality wood-finish flooring (Parquet) to add warmth and align with the brand's natural product concept. Strategic layout of ceiling spotlights to ensure even light distribution and highlight product details on the shelves. Technical Infrastructure: Completion of all electrical wiring, safety systems, and fire protection in full compliance with major shopping mall standards. Commitment to Excellence: Through this project, ELC Contracting demonstrated its ability to execute projects according to international franchise standards, ensuring a high-quality finish that enhances the customer’s shopping experience.",
